                            <comment id="14479759" author="paulk" created="Wed, 11 Jan 2012 05:50:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Possible patch attached. It is a little crude in that it runs the VariableScopeVisitor twice. It might be possible to come up with a more efficient alternate approach.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14479748" author="paulk" created="Wed, 11 Jan 2012 06:14:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;OK, a slightly nicer patch I think.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14479751" author="paulk" created="Fri, 13 Jan 2012 21:42:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Closures defined externally from the source unit being compiled didn&apos;t correctly access @Field fields. This should be fixed now. Thanks for spotting and reporting the problem.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
